item.title: Go 1.8 development stats
item.author: rakyll@rakyll.org (Jaana Burcu Dogan)
item.description: Go 1.8 is going to to launched in February 2017. There is a sizable list of new features and improvements on the release notes. While these notes is the best summary to see what has happened in the last 6 months, I will try to give you some stats to give you a sense of the size of the work. I have examined all the changes merged into the tree during the Go 1.
